<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_349_r1l20">Andres voyt von Ryneck <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_349_r1l21">Karlburg vnd Karlſtat </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_349_r1l22"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Andres als Jr vns aber <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des pferds <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_349_r1l23">etc das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch bey <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_349_r1l24">knecht / das pfeͣrd . daʒ man <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> knecht nehſt ſehen lıeſſ . ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_349_r1l25">haben wır mıt ~ den <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> wolfſtein dıe von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_349_r1l26">Beheim warn geredt . dıe eẅch auch <expan>ſchreıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> als Jr in irem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_349_r1l27">brıef den wır eẅch hıemıt <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> auch wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan> </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_350" id="174r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l1">Jſt nu das pfeͣrd eẅr ſo mugt Jr es behalten . wan wır <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſehen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l2">vns Jr ſeyt ın der <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nunft</expan> daʒ ır es da mıt wol wıſſet ʒu <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r1l3">als Jr pıllıch ſüllet / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> martinj </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_349" id="173v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Andres Voyt von Ryneck, <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> zu Karlburg und
                        Karlstat</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Andres, als ir uns aber
              <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des pferds <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
            etc., das haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
              <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch bey <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> knecht das
            pfeͣrd, daz man <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> knecht nehst sehen liess, so haben wir mit
            den <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> Wolfstein, die von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Beheim warn, geredt, die ewch auch
                <expan>schreibe<ex>n</ex></expan>, als ir in irem brief, den wir ewch hiemit
                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, auch wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan>. <pb facs="#facs_350" id="174r"/> Ist nu das pfeͣrd ewr, so mugt ir es behalten, wan wir
                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sehen</expan> uns, ir seyt in der
              <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nunft</expan>, daz ir es damit wol wisset zu
              <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan>, als ir pillich süllet. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Martini.</ab>
</div>
